oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Tintype of two unidentified men
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Tintype of two unidentified young men, seated next to one another. Both men are dressed in jackets, ties, vests, and are wearing hats. One of the men has his arm draped casually around the other man's shoulder. He holds a cigarette in his other hand. The second man has his hands crossed on his lap and has a cigarette in his mouth.
